5
00:00:22,337 --> 00:00:25,048
So you two ready
to find out the sex of this baby?

6
00:00:25,215 --> 00:00:26,257
- Yeah.
- Absolutely.

7
00:00:26,424 --> 00:00:29,844
Is Halley hoping
for a little brother or a little sister?

8
00:00:30,011 --> 00:00:34,682
Well, she's 9 months old. So unless it
jingles or is in my bra, she doesn't care.

9
00:00:36,017 --> 00:00:38,728
And how about you two?

10
00:00:38,895 --> 00:00:41,523
You know, for the first one,
we really wanted a girl.

11
00:00:41,689 --> 00:00:44,067
But this time around,
we don't have a preference.

12
00:00:44,234 --> 00:00:46,444
Yeah, boy, girl, as long as it's healthy.

13
00:00:46,611 --> 00:00:47,695
[ULTRASOUND HUMMING]

14
00:00:47,862 --> 00:00:50,448
Well, it's a boy.

15
00:00:51,533 --> 00:00:53,201
BOTH:
Oh.

16
00:00:54,661 --> 00:00:57,580
Oh, come on.
You can't really be disappointed.

17
00:00:57,747 --> 00:01:01,709
Hey, I barely know how to be a man myself.
Now I have to teach someone?

18
00:01:01,876 --> 00:01:05,463
As the saying goes,
"Those who can't do, teach."

19
00:01:06,798 --> 00:01:08,758
Don't you want a little version of Howard?

20
00:01:08,925 --> 00:01:11,886
